dwm
---

dynamic window manager, by suckless
more info on http://dwm.suckless.org

how to patch
---

`patch -p1 < filename.diff` to apply the patch
`patch -p1 -R < filename.diff` to revert the patch

how to install
---

install on archlinux: scrot pasystray NetworkManager st acpi xscreensaver
copy `dwm.desktop` to /usr/share/xsessions if using a graphical login (lightdm)
